{"tid":2178203,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【貪民自作孽】沉船後榴槤漂滿海！村民瘋搶 363人食後中毒塞爆醫院","createTime":"2020-08-28T08:37:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-28T12:14:24.000Z","uid":241764,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"615c7a6c77eb0dbd2e05c2c2a282d6fb15772fe2","tid":2178203,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T08:37:39.000Z","msg":"正所謂「病從口入」，但人類總是犯同樣的錯！廣西防城港東興市萬尾金灘海域本月26日，有一艘裝滿榴槤的走私貨船擱淺沉沒，導致大量榴槤在海上漂浮。當地村民獲悉後，紛紛開小艇前往打撈，還帶回家盡情享用。就在當晚至翌日早晨，當地超過300名村民因出現腹痛及屙嘔等症狀，先後擁到多家醫院求診，全部被診斷為食物中毒。當局事後追查，才發現這批民眾原來都曾進食過從萬尾海域撿拾回來的榴槤。<br />\n<br />\n全文: <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200828/YYPV6KBQY5HETF47YCKRPIOYC4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200828%2FYYPV6KBQY5HETF47YCKRPIOYC4&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyBzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=e4f49cca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200828%2FYYPV6KBQY5HETF47YCKRPIOYC4&h=fb8a8efe\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200828/YYPV6KBQY5HETF47YCKRPIOYC4</a>"},{"pid":"b3fe8fa879546c93507c4820f597d5e5a4748d5f","tid":2178203,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T11:23:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"343043140fe0543bad3a9e718f28b46c93ac8e77","tid":2178203,"uid":254504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T11:27:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05edd6b4644f9d12485598902ba705851fc8403a","tid":2178203,"uid":162539,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T11:29:20.000Z","msg":"硬係以為榴槤塞爆屎眼"},{"pid":"2938ccefdcf6732ca316e7c5f2a0bc